    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "We realised just before we merged this that it would be problematic with international keyboards. I think there are only three of our default shortcuts that will have problems - `shift+=`, `.` and `alt+-`. We're thinking about ways to handle it, including defining some shortcuts on the KeyPress event (which follows characters rather than keys), or just avoiding shortcuts on punctuation keys.\n"
  },
